  THE&NAME$FIELD. (NORMAL TSO NAMING CONVENTIONS APPLY.  ENCLOSE FULLY
  QUALIFIED DATASET NAMES IN SINGLE QUOTES)

  BY SPECIFYING AN&L$IN THE&TYPE OF NAME$FIELD,  AND ONE OR MORE INDEX LEVELS
  IN THE&NAME$FIELD, YOU CAN DISPLAY INFORMATION FOR ANY DISK DATASETS
  BEGINNING WITH THE SPECIFIED INDEX LEVEL(S).

